{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"673","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"慘澹3月 金控獲利大減六成","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: '>2020-04-11 01:01 </span><span style='font-family: '>經濟日報<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>本報綜合報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: '><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%AF%8C%E9%82%A6%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A9.JPG' style='width: 800px; height: 593px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: '>富邦金拿下單月、第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季純益與<span lang='EN-US'>EPS</span>三冠王。 （本報系資料庫）</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>金控獲利從二月豔陽天進入慘澹三月天，整體金控<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月在四家虧損下，單月獲利較前月大幅衰退近六成，累計第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季稅後純益<span lang='EN-US'>868</span>億元，與去年同期相當。冠軍富邦金是<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月唯一獲利較前月成長的金控，並一口氣拿下單月、第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季與累計每股稅後純益（<span lang='EN-US'>EPS</span>）三冠王，也是唯一<span lang='EN-US'>EPS</span>突破<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>元的金控。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>新冠肺炎疫情擴大衝擊全球資本市場<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月震盪，多家金控<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月獲利均較前月衰退，原因都脫不了財務操作「染疫」衍生評價損失。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>累計第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季獲利，除了核心子公司涵蓋壽險的民營金控富邦、國泰、中信、新光等四家，比去年同期有拉出相當幅度成長外，其他金控扣除合庫金比去年同期僅微增<span lang='EN-US'>0.44</span>億元，剩下十家都較去年衰退。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>華南、兆豐、開發、台新金<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月虧損，永豐、日盛與第一金賺不到億元，華南與開發金更因<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月慘虧導致第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季盈轉虧。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>富邦金<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月稅後純益<span lang='EN-US'>81.24</span>億元，較去年同月成長<span lang='EN-US'>83%</span>，也比<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>月逆勢成長<span lang='EN-US'>52%</span>，首季稅後純益<span lang='EN-US'>229.43</span>億元，年增<span lang='EN-US'>84%</span>，<span lang='EN-US'>EPS</span>為<span lang='EN-US'>2.24</span>元。主因富邦人壽<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月暴衝大賺<span lang='EN-US'>74.85</span>億元，較去年同期大幅成長<span lang='EN-US'>533%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>富邦金表示，富邦壽大賺因國內外投資處分利得及基金配息均較去年同期成長，只是市場波動下，<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月未實現利益也因此由正轉負。北富銀獲利則明顯下滑，<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月賺<span lang='EN-US'>2.47</span>億元，月減八成多，因市場波動衝擊操作。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>公股龍頭兆豐金<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月在國內外與股債波動夾擊下，核心兆豐銀財務操作評價損失大增，導致<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月出現罕見虧損。兆豐金自結<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月稅後淨損<span lang='EN-US'>15.65</span>億元，第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季稅後純益縮水至<span lang='EN-US'>19.29</span>億元，<span lang='EN-US'>EPS</span>為<span lang='EN-US'>0.14</span>元。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>第一金<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月獲利陡降至<span lang='EN-US'>0.76</span>億元，第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季賺<span lang='EN-US'>29.38</span>億元，年減<span lang='EN-US'>38.9%</span>，<span lang='EN-US'>EPS</span>為<span lang='EN-US'>0.24</span>元，同樣因核心的一銀<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月獲利受金融交易操作大衰退，加以其他證券、投信、壽險及創投等子公司單月都虧，因此獲利欠佳。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>華南金之前爆出華南永昌證權證避險不及大虧，已預知<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月虧損，昨天自結單月淨損<span lang='EN-US'>35.99</span>億元，累計第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季也盈轉虧，累計稅後淨損<span lang='EN-US'>14.48</span>億元，每股虧損<span lang='EN-US'>0.12</span>元。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>永豐金<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月只賺<span lang='EN-US'>200</span>萬元，雖然永豐銀行單月獲利成長，但受全球股市下跌衝擊，永豐金證券及創投，<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月分別虧損<span lang='EN-US'>2.05</span>億元、<span lang='EN-US'>4.18</span>億元，影響表現。台新金<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月淨損<span lang='EN-US'>1.5</span>億元，第<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>季賺<span lang='EN-US'>25.6</span>億元，年減<span lang='EN-US'>42%</span>，<span lang='EN-US'>EPS</span>為<span lang='EN-US'>0.2</span>元。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E6%AB%83%E9%87%91%E6%8E%A7%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A9.jpg' style='width: 650px; height: 920px;' />&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: '>圖／經濟日報提供</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: '>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: '>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>:https://udn.com/news/story/7252/4483660</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-04-13","clk_count":"171"}},"__N_SSG":true}